  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>In humble villages, a single glowstone often hangs above the hearth, casting a gentle radiance that warms the heart as much as the home. In noble estates, entire gardens shimmer with these enchanted stones, strung like stars to illuminate midnight feasts beneath their artificial constellations. Each stone begins as a dull brown, but when shaken vigorously, it blossoms with a golden glow—an echo Eeleeos, Elara’s celestial light.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activation</strong>: 1 action (manipulate, concentrate)<br /><strong>Frequency</strong>: Once per day<br /><strong>Duration</strong>: 12 hours</p><p><strong>Effect</strong>: When activated, the Glowstone sheds 10 feet of bright light and an additional 20 feet of dim light. The glow persists for 12 hours, providing a steady, magical illumination regardless of weather or surroundings.</p>"
